    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1916-04-29T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1916-04-29T00:00:00-05:00" n="1206"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1206">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 872.48/71</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in France</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_SWG1"
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Sharp</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-04-29">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 29, 1916</hi>
                        </date>.<lb/>[<hi rend="italic">Received 12.05 p. m.</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1375. For Red Cross:</p>
                <quote rend="blockquote">
                    <p>Expect favorable decision material Marseille. Suggest no more material be
                        sent this way. French authorities to make special exception in this case.
                        They refuse on account blockade to allow further relief Serbia. Possibility
                        free transportation in France will be refused, although still hopeful.
                        Leaving for Berne about Monday to arrange further transportation.</p>
                    <p rend="right">
                        <persName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Ryan</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </p>
                </quote>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_SWG1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Sharp</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
